Cardiac surgery in patients with Hemophilia:is it safe?

Shalabi A(1)(2)(3)(4), Kachel E(5)(6)(7), Kogan A(5), Sternik L(5), 
Grosman-Rimon L(6)(7), Ben-Avi R(6)(7), Ghanem D(6)(7), Ram E(5), Raanani E(5), 
